</taxonomicName>
W.B. Liao &amp; Q. Fan (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.197.1.2" author="Fan, Q" journalOrPublisher="Phytotaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" pagination="15 - 26" refId="B4" refString="Fan, Q, Chen, SF, Wang, LY, Chen, ZX, Liao, WB, 2015. A new species and new section of Viola (Violaceae) from Guangdong, China. Phytotaxa 197 (1): 15 - 26, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.197.1.2" title="A new species and new section of Viola (Violaceae) from Guangdong, China." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.197.1.2" volume="197" year="2015">Fan et al. 2015</bibRefCitation>
